  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e1421e71510ca48e4f4399",
      "text": "本日の教訓 2026-04-17 suto3",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370214,
      "updated": 1776370214
    },
    {
      "id": "69e149a000000000002495f7",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/02b69d90ee5795822778dda635b05b7b]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776372129,
      "updated": 1776372130
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1422500000000002495ec",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370214,
      "updated": 1776370230
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1423600000000002495ef",
      "text": " [トピック指向]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370231,
      "updated": 1776370262
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1434d00000000002495f2",
      "text": "　 書き込み先を「[トピック]（[話題]）」の単位で作り、その話題に関することを書き込んでいく手法",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370510,
      "updated": 1776370618
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1434f00000000002495f3",
      "text": "  目的を達成するために必要な情報を見つけやすい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370511,
      "updated": 1776370519
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1438d00000000002495f5",
      "text": "  対義語はブック指向？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370573,
      "updated": 1776370602
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1434f00000000002495f4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370511,
      "updated": 1776370513
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1424600000000002495f0",
      "text": " [トピック指向日記]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370247,
      "updated": 1776370523
    },
    {
      "id": "69e151d100000000001204a9",
      "text": " 　元ページが消えているのでよくわからん",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776374225,
      "updated": 1776374257
    },
    {
      "id": "69e151fc00000000001204aa",
      "text": " 　トピック単位で日記を作ること？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776374269,
      "updated": 1776374315
    },
    {
      "id": "69e160210000000000df98dc",
      "text": " 　infobox日記はトピック指向日記？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776377889,
      "updated": 1776377915
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1428600000000002495f1",
      "text": "　 [日付タグ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370311,
      "updated": 1776374263
    },
    {
      "id": "69e144bf00000000002495f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776370880,
      "updated": 1776370880
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1796d000000000009a850",
      "text": " もう数年来、井戸端日記は重たくてスケールしなくて大変なことになっている（現在進行系）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776384366,
      "updated": 1776384459
    },
    {
      "id": "69e179d5000000000009a851",
      "text": "  もうその場しのぎの方法では解決しないから infobox日記 へ移行しましょうというのはひとつの意見",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776384470,
      "updated": 1776384565
    },
    {
      "id": "69e17a36000000000009a852",
      "text": "  　自分は特に困っていないから変える必要はない、という意見もある [ブラケティング禁止.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776384566,
      "updated": 1776384658
    },
    {
      "id": "69e17aa4000000000009a853",
      "text": "  　　これは、ある程度のパワーユーザーで、重い井戸端日記を読み書きするのが苦にならないのだろう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776384676,
      "updated": 1776384810
    },
    {
      "id": "69e17b2c000000000009a854",
      "text": "  　　逆にいえば、ライトユーザーを切り捨てているのが現在の井戸端",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776384812,
      "updated": 1776384878
    },
    {
      "id": "69e17b83000000000009a855",
      "text": "  　　アクティブメンバー、新規メンバー ともに減ってきているし",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776384899,
      "updated": 1776384951
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1796b000000000009a84f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776384363,
      "updated": 1776384363
    },
    {
      "id": "69e14b600000000000ab2da7",
      "text": "　[日記ページをどのように作っている？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776372576,
      "updated": 1776372586
    },
    {
      "id": "69e14b620000000000ab2da8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776372578,
      "updated": 1776372579
    },
    {
      "id": "69e17094000000000009a84c",
      "text": "　[トピック指向文芸的データベース]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776382100,
      "updated": 1776397671
    },
    {
      "id": "69e17096000000000009a84d",
      "text": "　　という電波を受信",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776382102,
      "updated": 1776382123
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1709a000000000009a84e",
      "text": "  [トピック指向日記]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776382106,
      "updated": 1776402908
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1c1d30000000000c51266",
      "text": "  [トピック指向用語集]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776402900,
      "updated": 1776402910
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1c1d30000000000c51267",
      "text": "  [トピック指向ブックマーク]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776402900,
      "updated": 1776423657
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1c1ee0000000000c51268",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776402927,
      "updated": 1776402927
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f4630000000000f14f47",
      "text": "　ライトユーザーを切り捨てているのが現在の井戸端",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776415843,
      "updated": 1776415845
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f4650000000000f14f48",
      "text": "　　大事なことなので２回言いました",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776415846,
      "updated": 1776415867
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f3440000000000f14f43",
      "text": " 「井戸端日記に転載禁止」は機能するか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776415557,
      "updated": 1776415727
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f3680000000000f14f44",
      "text": " 　たぶん無理そう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776415593,
      "updated": 1776415608
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f3790000000000f14f45",
      "text": " 　　自分のCosenseに関する不満は、（Cosenseの哲学に反する）アクセス権限周りのことが多いな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776415610,
      "updated": 1776415715
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f3fc0000000000f14f46",
      "text": " 　あれも禁止、これも禁止ではうまく回らなくなる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776415740,
      "updated": 1776415783
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1c1d10000000000c51264",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776402898,
      "updated": 1776402898
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f9bf000000000088364f",
      "text": "　井戸端日記しか見てない勢って何人ぐらいいるのだろう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776417216,
      "updated": 1776417268
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1f9ca0000000000883650",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776417226,
      "updated": 1776417228
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1faba0000000000883651",
      "text": "　適度な粒度で悪口が言えるようになりたい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776417468,
      "updated": 1776417499
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1fabb0000000000883652",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776417468,
      "updated": 1776417468
    },
    {
